comments: I noticed that the first part of the word identified the type of shape, and the second part of the word identified the color, but I was unable to remember which was which. The hard part of the study was that the shapes and words flashed so fast that I did not have enough time to let my brain make a connection between the first part of the word and the shape and between the next part of the word and the color. I was only able to remember that anything starting with buvee was a pentagon.
